WEBVTT

00:02.797 --> 00:05.277
<i>Here's another Valentine's Day favorite.</i>

00:06.333 --> 00:08.200
♪ Love ♪

00:08.269 --> 00:10.602
♪ Love will keep us together... ♪

00:10.671 --> 00:12.704
<i>Nope. I've got
enough things annoying me.</i>

00:12.773 --> 00:14.206
<i>And there's one right there.</i>

00:14.275 --> 00:16.408
<i>Oliver clearly has a problem
he wants to share,</i>

00:16.477 --> 00:17.910
<i>but he needs me to pull it out of him.</i>

00:17.978 --> 00:19.047
<i>Watch.</i>

00:19.072 --> 00:20.450
Everything okay?

00:20.475 --> 00:22.047
Never better.

00:23.484 --> 00:24.783
Taylor has something she wants to ask me

00:24.852 --> 00:26.151
but is afraid I'll say no.

00:26.220 --> 00:28.187
If I seem agitated,
she'll wait till later.

00:28.255 --> 00:31.290
- Hey, Mom.
- Ohh! Just great!

00:33.494 --> 00:36.562
<i>And my sweet little annoyance number 3.</i>

00:36.630 --> 00:39.998
Anna-Kat, you don't need to spend
10 minutes on each Valentine card.

00:40.067 --> 00:42.201
But I want them to be nice
for kids in my class.

00:42.269 --> 00:44.136
Daddy said I should
take pride in my work.

00:44.205 --> 00:45.604
But that's not for stupid stuff,

00:45.673 --> 00:47.105
like made-up holidays.

00:47.174 --> 00:49.675
<i>Manufactured romance
is just not my thing.</i>

00:49.743 --> 00:52.277
<i>I don't have the gene for it...
unlike some people.</i>

00:52.346 --> 00:54.079
Happy Valentine's Day.

00:54.148 --> 00:56.181
- Oh. To you, too, baby.
- Mm.

00:56.250 --> 00:57.449
So, Taylor tells me...

00:57.518 --> 00:58.684
We've got to go,
or I'll be late for volleyball!

00:58.752 --> 01:00.352
I'm team captain!
Team captain can't be late!

01:00.421 --> 01:01.887
Geez, Taylor.

01:01.956 --> 01:03.021
Let's save that level of panic

01:03.090 --> 01:04.256
for the first time you miss your period.

01:04.325 --> 01:06.959
Come on, let's move it, people.

01:07.027 --> 01:09.027
I know you have to write
your book proposal,

01:09.096 --> 01:11.430
so don't feel like you need to do
anything big for me this year.

01:11.498 --> 01:12.998
Big? What ever do you mean?

