01:36.457 --> 01:39.191
Seriously, a card is all I need.

01:40.227 --> 01:41.460
Card it is.

01:41.528 --> 01:43.221
<i>He's got something planned.</i>

01:43.307 --> 01:45.097
<i>Why couldn't he embrace
a more meaningful holiday?</i>

01:45.165 --> 01:46.900
<i>Groundhog Day is totally underrated.</i>

